spread the word that you're

00:00:53.370 --> 00:00:55.951
ready and want jobs
for babysitting.

00:00:55.951 --> 00:00:57.700
-So once your parents
have spread the word

00:00:57.700 --> 00:00:59.600
and you finally get
a babysitting job,

00:00:59.600 --> 00:01:02.730
it's very important that you
ask the questions, like, what's

00:01:02.730 --> 00:01:05.400
their schedule, what's
their bedtime routine, what

00:01:05.400 --> 00:01:07.500
do they eat, are
there any allergies?

00:01:07.500 --> 00:01:11.230
-It makes you seem like
a responsible, interested

00:01:11.230 --> 00:01:12.200
babysitter.

00:01:12.200 --> 00:01:14.670
