like you more because you're

00:01:14.670 --> 00:01:16.044
on the ball and
you know what all

00:01:16.044 --> 00:01:17.660
of the kid's needs
and wants are.

00:01:17.660 --> 00:01:18.725
So it'd be good.

00:01:18.725 --> 00:01:19.225
-Yeah.

00:01:19.225 --> 00:01:23.270
So it's very important for you
to be the one asking questions.

00:01:23.270 --> 00:01:25.770
-So when the parents
leave, try to get

00:01:25.770 --> 00:01:28.670
to know the kids-- like
their ages, their names--

00:01:28.670 --> 00:01:30.900
so they feel more
comfortable around you.

00:01:30.900 --> 00:01:33.720
And be their friend, be
cheerful, make them happy,

00:01:33.720 --> 00:01:36.406
do something funny,
so they feel like they

00:01:36.406 --> 00:01:37.530
can get to know you better.

00:01:37.530 --> 00:01:40.820
-But also make sure that they
know that you mean business.

00:01:40.820 --> 00:01:43.610
-So you're not all fun
